                <p class="work-card-desc">
                    Led monolith-to-microservices migration with key architectural decisions.
                    Image similarity search via PostgreSQL + pgvector with 15x SIMD speedup.
                </p>

                <details class="expandable">
                    <summary class="expandable-trigger">
                        <span class="material-icons expandable-icon">expand_more</span>
